(1, 'DEPUTY MANAGER (STRUCTURAL ENGINEER), DESIGN & DEVELOPMENT', 3.00, 'Part-time', '8-10 Years', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Job Summary:</span><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">The Structural Engineer is responsible for designing, planning, and overseeing the construction of buildings and infrastructure projects. This role ensures that structures are safe, stable, and compliant with local regulations and standards.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><u>Key Responsibilities:</u></span><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Design and Analysis:</span><span style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Develop structural designs for residential and commercial buildings.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Perform structural analysis using software like ETABS, SAP2000, STAAD Pro, etc.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Create detailed drawings and specifications for construction.</li></ul><p><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Project Management:</span><span style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Collaborate with architects, construction managers, and other engineers.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Review and approve project designs and construction plans.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Ensure projects are completed on time, within budget, and to the specified quality standards.</li></ul><p><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Site Supervision:</span><span style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Inspect construction sites to monitor progress and ensure adherence to design specifications and safety standards.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Conduct site visits and inspections to identify and resolve any structural issues.</li></ul><p><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Compliance and Standards:</span><span style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Ensure all designs comply with local building codes, regulations, and standards.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Prepare and submit necessary documentation for government approvals and permits.</li></ul><p><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Problem-Solving:</span><span style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Identify structural issues and provide effective solutions.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Investigate structural failures and recommend corrective actions.</li></ul><p><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Client Liaison:</span><span style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Communicate with clients to understand their needs and provide regular updates on project progress.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Offer technical advice and solutions to clients and stakeholders.</li></ul><p><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Documentation and Reporting:</span><span style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Maintain detailed records of design calculations, construction procedures, and inspection results.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Prepare reports and presentations for project stakeholders.</li></ul><p><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><u>Qualifications and Skills:</u></span><span style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Bachelor’s degree in Civil or Structural Engineering.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">-Minimum of 8-10 years of experience in structural engineering, preferably within the real estate sector or from a reputed consultancy firm.</li></ul><p><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><u>Additional Requirements:</u></span><span style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: none;\">- Proficiency in structural design software (e.g., ETABS, SAP2000, STAAD Pro), AutoCAD, and other relevant tools.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">- Strong understanding of local building codes, standards, and regulations.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">- Excellent problem-solving abilities, strong communication skills, and the ability to work effectively in a team.</li></ul><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"list-style: none;\">- SEng or ECPS enlisted engineers or equivalent certification is preferred.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">- Proficiency in both Bangla and English.</li><li style=\"list-style: none;\">- Ability to work in both office and field environments, with occasional visit to construction sites around Dhaka City.</li></ul><p><br style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Deadline:</span><span style=\"color: rgb(27, 29, 29); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;June 30, 2024</span><br></p>', '2024-07-25 16:43:54', '2024-07-25 17:08:33'),
